$NetBSD: patch-ah,v 1.4 2005/03/15 15:58:52 wennmach Exp $

Install nnpfs_mod.o into $(lkmdir), not $(bindir).
Do not strip nnpfs_mod.o while installing it.

--- nnpfs/bsd/Makefile.in.orig	2004-07-20 07:28:23.000000000 -0400
+++ nnpfs/bsd/Makefile.in	2004-12-22 20:32:06.000000000 -0500
